{"tid":116880,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"[拋磚引玉] 聖地巡禮交流","createTime":"2017-02-11T17:48:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-12T06:28:56.000Z","uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cd8465e9b40c33744081b9f86d0e783b954e85ea","tid":116880,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T17:48:44.000Z","msg":"之前見到有巴打做開聖地巡禮嘅研究，發覺呢度定隔離登都好少交流聖地巡禮嘅post（係間唔中有巴絲打出下遊記咁）<br />\n<br />\n所以想開個post拋磚引玉，等自己同大家都曬下戰績，順便交流下心得啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲有寫埋搭車方法同難度(一星最易，五星最難），等大家有個譜咁啦<br />\n<br />\n我自己之前一兩年都去過一啲聖地，主要都係京阿尼嘅作品(Kyoto Animation)，因為佢作畫靚又夠逼真，去都去得有feel啲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過講明先，我自己當然去唔曬所有地方，咁就有勞其他去過聖巡嘅巴絲打幫下手分享下，同埋由於有時一堆聖地分開咗兩次去，所以請原諒我唔係好似遊記咁寫曬嗰日發生嘅事。<br />\n<br />\n1. K-ON<br />\nK-ON嘅景點不外乎兩個地方，豐鄉小學校同京都市內各地<br />\n<br />\n豐鄉小學校<br />\n唔少巴打應該都去過豐鄉，我自己本身都去過兩次，一次係舊年，一次係3年前<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/o7unc4q5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fo7unc4q5&h=e4421f75&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2863rxce\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2863rxce&h=e7419b23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/6yqj0upa\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F6yqj0upa&h=11520f97&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n舊年去嗰次真係可能撞正假期，所以幾熱鬧，除咗本地人之外仲有啲係東京嗰邊揸車過去玩cosplay<br />\n<br />\n自己嚟講主力係最高嗰層嘅音樂室（輕音部個室）<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/o1zxnrdl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fo1zxnrdl&h=2ae24824&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n因為入面裝飾到同K-ON入面嘅場景一模一樣<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9kbdsf6i\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9kbdsf6i&h=c3905cd5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/pd8o451i\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fpd8o451i&h=9c1e1a32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5roc0u6k\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5roc0u6k&h=b3135d24&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另一個主力係隔離嗰個小舞台（即係Mio fans club茶敘嗰度）<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/482lnick\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F482lnick&h=5635b1b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n學校天台（でもね、会えたよ。素敵な子猫に）<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/28d3k6z9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F28d3k6z9&h=90da053b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n走廊<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xubf2095\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxubf2095&h=94349e30&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n劇場版入面幾個主角傾計嗰個位（無記錯嘅話）<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/t9ck1y2a\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ft9ck1y2a&h=bcd60296&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n學校禮堂（開live嘅地方）<br />\n我舊年去嗰陣撞正有人搞活動，所以唯有up前年啲舊相<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/9e3m4thr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F9e3m4thr&h=68b66b2b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然仲有入面嘅觀光案內所，因為擺滿晒好多K-ON擁躉送嘅精品<br />\n不過好似係要假期先開<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/spv0qlon\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fspv0qlon&h=96a92eac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/gce0yfnm\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fgce0yfnm&h=6cf336e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/u31wqsj5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fu31wqsj5&h=b4564aeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n動畫入面嘅豚ちゃん現實入面變咗麵包<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/tdy9mfp6\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Ftdy9mfp6&h=bccd3c85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其他<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/bsgnw6ke\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbsgnw6ke&h=05b50608&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dbolihps\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdbolihps&h=bfb6a33c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n交通<br />\nJR京都線/琵琶湖線新快速火車<br />\n一係就近江八幡站轉近江鐵路米原/彦根方向列車，冇嘅話就跳上一架去八日市站轉車<br />\n一係就彦根站轉近江鐵路八日市／貴生川方向列車<br />\n或者JR新幹線去到米原轉近江鐵路八日市／貴生川方向列車<br />\n<br />\n方便度：***<br />\n去開日本啲鄉下地方嘅話其實無乜難度，但新手就會覺得麻煩。難就難喺近江鐵路啲班次，始終鄉下地方，火車比較疏，所以最好查清楚班次表同預鬆少少時間"},{"pid":"3aff95fbebe1903248da8e0ad55c64d0b005eabd","tid":116880,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T17:51:43.000Z","msg":"我去左大土金"},{"pid":"aa400b0e9aa6e47c261585b095d9d75697a19eb7","tid":116880,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T17:52:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我去左大土金</blockquote><br />\n手殘撳左下揀字send左出去"},{"pid":"0e2bd88e331ac887a68fec3fe346b7c4708c2787","tid":116880,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T17:55:58.000Z","msg":"我去左大嶼山 發覺冇高達睇<br />\n<br />\nBtw<br />\n之前係對面見到有人睇完百變小櫻去返香港一樣既地方影返個分鏡<br />\n<br />\n諗起唔少動畫都有香港場景例如rod,fmp <br />\n係香港聖巡有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9ccce050371752fac0cb74102909a62b9285280","tid":116880,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T17:59:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我去左大嶼山 發覺冇高達睇<br />\n<br />\nBtw<br />\n之前係對面見到有人睇完百變小櫻去返香港一樣既地方影返個分鏡<br />\n<br />\n諗起唔少動畫都有香港場景例如rod,fmp <br />\n係香港聖巡有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聖巡呢啲嘢唔只限日本嘅<br />\n我都好希望有更加多動畫喺香港取景<br />\n聖巡都方便好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a04a500aac1c0180dd1c8294ce8b0f4f5c7f4ce","tid":116880,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T18:01:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我去左大嶼山 發覺冇高達睇<br />\n<br />\nBtw<br />\n之前係對面見到有人睇完百變小櫻去返香港一樣既地方影返個分鏡<br />\n<br />\n諗起唔少動畫都有香港場景例如rod,fmp <br />\n係香港聖巡有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聖巡呢啲嘢唔只限日本嘅<br />\n我都好希望有更加多動畫喺香港取景<br />\n聖巡都方便好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n記得之前有位呀清去左倫敦聖巡（冇記錯好似都係k-on <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d361e59a5fe1cdf30db9afbfb6697e274df35c7","tid":116880,"uid":606,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T18:16:16.000Z","msg":"巴打有冇去中二病個度<br />\n上年同個fd 兩條友淋住雨踩單車入去<br />\n我個人覺得算係一個比較難去嘅聖巡地點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45350cc492305250f0312cda6c51dd8c238dcb5e","tid":116880,"uid":34622,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T18:18:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我去左大嶼山 發覺冇高達睇<br />\n<br />\nBtw<br />\n之前係對面見到有人睇完百變小櫻去返香港一樣既地方影返個分鏡<br />\n<br />\n諗起唔少動畫都有香港場景例如rod,fmp <br />\n係香港聖巡有冇得諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n聖巡呢啲嘢唔只限日本嘅<br />\n我都好希望有更加多動畫喺香港取景<br />\n聖巡都方便好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有, 之前去過九龍公園(?)睇數碼暴龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/35.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a8cde88117c55cdee7f4086cc77cd749140c2b8","tid":116880,"uid":34135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T18:29:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/ob24ardq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fob24ardq&h=3782fc79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n京都鴨川<br />\n玉子市場<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dpbmlave\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdpbmlave&h=2e0d96ac&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n宇治<br />\n響け<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0798fd1f334d5f852baeddb09d72f3bbfc1e4e61","tid":116880,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T18:42:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打有冇去中二病個度<br />\n上年同個fd 兩條友淋住雨踩單車入去<br />\n我個人覺得算係一個比較難去嘅聖巡地點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n學校嗰個？"},{"pid":"f5d1a7a6af053742f4b0fe4b280326c1eae73ccc","tid":116880,"uid":200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T19:29:58.000Z","msg":"其實間學校係咪真係有人讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係的話男女比例會唔會9:1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7543c796d5c8c48acd031824335ac6ef71203135","tid":116880,"uid":3342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T19:36:29.000Z","msg":"Fate/zero<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8J9B5u3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8J9B5u3.jpg&h=72eb2e14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAngel beats<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/39255SF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F39255SF.jpg&h=893d8210&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n寒蟬<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/12/033529_e330e4fcb2351aab9923faef34de0d3f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F12%2F033529_e330e4fcb2351aab9923faef34de0d3f.jpg&h=0fe43830&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n冰菓<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/J7Ga38c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJ7Ga38c.jpg&h=21d299eb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1c7ccdbb9ff9d6ff87a08fc3ae04e6980c459821","tid":116880,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T20:19:46.000Z","msg":"京都市<br />\nK-ON除咗豐鄉之外，絕大部分都喺京都市取景<br />\n唔似豐鄉咁，呢啲景點有唔少都好零碎<br />\n同埋始終都過咗都起碼6年，入面有好多嘢都開始變樣<br />\n<br />\n叡電修學院站：mugi落車嘅地方<br />\n難度：*<br />\n交通：叡山電車修學院站落車<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/rlsb0ju7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Frlsb0ju7&h=9f517325&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xb1sp2ca\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxb1sp2ca&h=8652cc99&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xjq2lczw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxjq2lczw&h=d10e9d41&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/xjywfmd0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fxjywfmd0&h=4cc28489&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n附近嘅橋就係佢地劇場版放學行經嘅場景<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/0ezywhaq\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F0ezywhaq&h=8769bfb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/1axryq2e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F1axryq2e&h=e8bea90f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實冇幾遠係唯屋企附近嘅取材地，不過民居就無謂影喇<br />\n<br />\n宝ヶ池公園：梓貓新生歡迎會嘅地方<br />\n難度：**<br />\n（個公園唔難去，係佢取景嗰part比較偏僻少少，預咗要行多啲路，同埋個公園入面啲路係山路為主，最好著啲舒服少少嘅鞋）<br />\n交通：成個公園來講，應該係國際會館地鐵站落車嘅，不過松ヶ崎地鐵站行上山嗰邊會比較直接啲同快啲<br />\n<br />\nGoogle Map: <a href=\"https://www.google.com.hk/maps/place/%E3%82%BF%E3%82%A4%E3%83%A0%E3%82%BA%E5%AE%9D%E3%81%8C%E6%B1%A0%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E7%8B%90%E5%9D%82/@35.0571442,135.7760935,15z/data=!4m5!3m4!1s0x0:0x58b0b60a220505b7!8m2!3d35.0575205!4d135.7777199\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com.hk%2Fmaps%2Fplace%2F%25E3%2582%25BF%25E3%2582%25A4%25E3%2583%25A0%25E3%2582%25BA%25E5%25AE%259D%25E3%2581%258C%25E6%25B1%25A0%25E5%2585%25AC%25E5%259C%2592%25E7%258B%2590%25E5%259D%2582%2F%4035.0571442%2C135.7760935%2C15z%2Fdata%3D%214m5%213m4%211s0x0%3A0x58b0b60a220505b7%218m2%213d35.0575205%214d135.7777199&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=a7b0636f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com.hk/maps/place/%E3%82%BF%E3%82%A4%E3%83%A0%E3%82%BA%E5%AE%9D%E3%81%8C%E6%B1%A0%E5%85%AC%E5%9C%92%E7%8B%90%E5%9D%82/@35.0571442,135.7760935,15z/data=!4m5!3m4!1s0x0:0x58b0b60a220505b7!8m2!3d35.0575205!4d135.7777199</a><br />\n<br />\n京都國際會館<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/oxvq0ucd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Foxvq0ucd&h=a84ddadc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n園内遊船<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dk9chv4n\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdk9chv4n&h=0b60bb32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n租艇間屋，不過無開<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/dav01muz\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fdav01muz&h=a374fc05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMio訓示輕音部眾人嗰個地方<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/smhd1wyk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fsmhd1wyk&h=04f3551a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/anw903rd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fanw903rd&h=b9099a2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n三条名店街：唯買結他嗰度<br />\n難度：*<br />\n交通：京都市役所前地鐵站向南行或者經河原町三条嘅巴士<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/5c7tmi9h\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F5c7tmi9h&h=62781e06&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/vn0pxqoi\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fvn0pxqoi&h=ed8be7fa&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"eb8f3e4d449c98d8173d6a3f431ff1dc6d299ebb","tid":116880,"uid":55732,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T20:23:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實間學校係咪真係有人讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係的話男女比例會唔會9:1<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nK-ON取景嗰個係小學嘅舊校舍，啲學生喺後面新校舍上堂<br />\n而家棟嘢變咗做社區會堂，托兒所同圖書館<br />\n同埋俾啲好似我呢啲咁嘅毒撚朝聖嘅地方<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65bcb68e1ba120878c8f5cfcda4f4940f9da966c","tid":116880,"uid":53880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-11T22:45:18.000Z","msg":"之前順路去左橫須賀一轉<br />\n去左睇下はいふり啲場景<br />\n相就冇乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過果時就跟呢個map行左陣<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1dAoFpnYQj7xxSV9aJZRj6k0Mpfk&amp;hl=en_US&amp;ll=35.283668836746834%2C139.66369796910408&amp;z=16\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.google.com%2Fmaps%2Fd%2Fviewer%3Fmid%3D1dAoFpnYQj7xxSV9aJZRj6k0Mpfk%26hl%3Den_US%26ll%3D35.283668836746834%252C139.66369796910408%26z%3D16&d=jM2msIR27xdcbllsFNIWhNtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=5045582b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.google.com/maps/d/viewer?mid=1dAoFpnYQj7xxSV9aJZRj6k0Mpfk&amp;hl=en_US&amp;ll=35.283668836746834%2C139.66369796910408&amp;z=16</a><br />\n<br />\n如果去開東京既 可以過琦玉果面都大把聖巡"},{"pid":"50cb02b0cbea05f204536557af3b4e25f8946bab","tid":116880,"uid":1587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-12T04:37:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都想去聖巡，可能下年<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/norma